{"tid":2388482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾南山：若不積極防控，黑龍江2月底會有13萬人感染","createTime":"2021-01-31T07:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T09:22:57.000Z","uid":350584,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6c055ae619c0009e979f06bb6f48d66f2e54f2","tid":2388482,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"中國工程院院士鍾南山今日（31日）指，近日內地局部出現了集聚性的感染，說明在一定程度上放鬆了警惕，又指目前基層的病毒檢測能力比較薄弱，要借助先進科技，幫助基層提升能力，「將滅火變成防火」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他還表示，河北、黑龍江、吉林若從三級防控提升到二級防控，則有可能二月上旬就能被基本控制疫情；相反若不採取積極的防控措施，黑龍江到2月底可能就會有13萬人被感染。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/581604/新冠肺炎-鍾南山-若不積極防控-黑龍江2月底會有13萬人感染\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F581604%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%8D%BE%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1-%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7-%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%8D%E6%B1%9F2%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%8913%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=d6bc1824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/581604/新冠肺炎-鍾南山-若不積極防控-黑龍江2月底會有13萬人感染</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655dc0fd475f5a2fc19cd55e16f30b0defd8dfb5","tid":2388482,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"鍾南山稱，「我們與另外一個大學合作開展研究，他們醫學預測的研究模型相當可靠，在政府強力地干預下，要是從三級防控提升到二級防控，感染率可以降低20%&mdash;30%，估計這三個地方疫情在2月份就可以基本得到控制。」但是，假如不採取積極的防控措施，黑龍江2月底將有13萬人感染，河北2月底將有12萬人感染，「這個就不得了了。」<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，黑龍江昨日（30日）新增確診病例9宗，當日新增無症狀感染者4宗，現有確診病例500宗，現有無症狀感染者539宗。河北昨日新增1宗本地確診病例，為石家莊市報告。河北現有本地確診病例437宗，尚在醫學觀察本地無症狀感染者40宗。"},{"pid":"04b14c7869067f023905d991b236902fa3b0d168","tid":2388482,"uid":178875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"減13萬人口= 0感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bc13e37c3234c1eebb8d5366023d7c9bc90ba9","tid":2388482,"uid":11978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"一級防控=火葬場ot？"},{"pid":"b360d454e6d514e28957fda8884537cbc48d53a4","tid":2388482,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"中共：黑龍江不屬於中國"},{"pid":"5b112b105135f320ca512113578e8aaa2b353ecb","tid":2388482,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"日本仔生化武器？"},{"pid":"f3bac00c89c56e130cddd71807d503b1821f4d4f","tid":2388482,"uid":340189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"19e3c038c09a9796b7c789937b5868906fd36246","tid":2388482,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"又話清零<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d7640b54e096d1f64e9302f84ec27bc823a583","tid":2388482,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />核平"},{"pid":"82ac5d18622e7f4e751e8f6866ea3ceb377907de","tid":2388482,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:55:51.000Z","msg":"疫情可防可控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bdbff2060ddae8e8bcc6babe0cdcb3c28b6e2d","tid":2388482,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"預定13萬人感染<br />\n厲害"},{"pid":"c7af2bf7ec68f8a2ae73ce26b9e3825a171ace85","tid":2388482,"uid":33522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"盧寵物而家準備